#. <section class="sutta" id="sn55.34"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn55.34:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 55"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 55"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn55.34:0.2"
msgid "4. Puññābhisandavagga"
msgstr "4. Overflowing Merit"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn55.34:0.3"
msgid "34. Paṭhamadevapadasutta"
msgstr "34. Footprints of the Gods (1st)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.34:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn55.34:1.2"
msgid ""
"“Cattārimāni, bhikkhave, devānaṃ devapadāni avisuddhānaṃ sattānaṃ visuddhiyā "
"apariyodātānaṃ sattānaṃ pariyodapanāya."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, these four footprints of the gods are in order to purify "
"unpurified beings and cleanse unclean beings."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.34:2.1"
msgid "Katamāni cattāri?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "sn55.34:2.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ariyasāvako buddhe aveccappasādena samannāgato hoti—"
msgstr "Firstly, a noble disciple has experiential confidence in the Buddha …"

msgctxt "sn55.34:2.3"
msgid "itipi so bhagavā … pe … satthā devamanussānaṃ buddho bhagavāti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn55.34:2.4"
msgid ""
"Idaṃ paṭhamaṃ devānaṃ devapadaṃ avisuddhānaṃ sattānaṃ visuddhiyā "
"apariyodātānaṃ sattānaṃ pariyodapanāya."
msgstr ""
"This is the first footprint of the gods in order to purify unpurified beings "
"and cleanse unclean beings."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.393"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.34:3.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, ariyasāvako dhamme … pe …"
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, a noble disciple has experiential confidence in the teaching …"

msgctxt "sn55.34:3.2"
msgid "saṅghe … pe …."
msgstr "the Saṅgha …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn55.34:4.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, ariyasāvako ariyakantehi sīlehi samannāgato hoti "
"akhaṇḍehi … pe … samādhisaṃvattanikehi."
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, a noble disciple’s ethical conduct is loved by the noble ones, "
"unbroken, impeccable, spotless, and unmarred, liberating, praised by "
"sensible people, not mistaken, and leading to immersion."

msgctxt "sn55.34:4.2"
msgid ""
"Idaṃ catutthaṃ devānaṃ devapadaṃ avisuddhānaṃ sattānaṃ visuddhiyā "
"apariyodātānaṃ sattānaṃ pariyodapanāya."
msgstr ""
"This is the fourth footprint of the gods in order to purify unpurified "
"beings and cleanse unclean beings."

msgctxt "sn55.34:4.3"
msgid ""
"Imāni kho, bhikkhave, cattāri devānaṃ devapadāni avisuddhānaṃ sattānaṃ "
"visuddhiyā apariyodātānaṃ sattānaṃ pariyodapanāyā”ti."
msgstr ""
"These four footprints of the gods are in order to purify unpurified beings "
"and cleanse unclean beings.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn55.34:4.4"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
